title: Team Insurgency looking for 5 man roster (OOL)

embed.description: Team Insurgency is a new Oceanic League of Legends team, currently looking for players.

body:
Team Insurgency is looking for players for Oceanic Open Ladder.

Currently all 5 slots are open for application and we require a full roster.

Prioritization of application is determined by multiple factors, including.

Ranking
Team Manner
Synergy with others
Determination to learn
And availability

Applications can be made directly through the site either through the application page or through the apply button on home page of the site at

https://www.teaminsurgency.com

After this we will be going through applications and contacting those chosen.

Look forward to seeing your applications.
